pageTitle: Itinerary for Wednesday, February 15, 2017 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Wednesday, February 15, 2017:

Ottawa, Ontario

9:30 a.m. The Prime Minister will attend the National Caucus meeting.

12:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will depart for Strasbourg, France.

Canada Reception Centre (Hangar 11)
Macdonald-Cartier International Airport
Ottawa, Ontario

Notes for media:

  • Photo opportunity for departure.
  • Media should arrive no later than 11:00 a.m.
